Implemented a new admin-gate edge function and wired config to enable admin JWT handling. The function validates JWTs, verifies admin role, supports login/logout/validate actions with MFA checks, creates and revokes admin sessions, and logs admin actions. Updated supabase/config.toml to register the admin-gate function and allow JWT handling.

